detailedDescription.articleBody: Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj International Airport, Mumbai, formerly known as Sahar International Airport, is the primary international airport serving the Mumbai Metropolitan Area, India.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Indira Gandhi International Airport is an airport located in the city of Delhi, India that serves as the international aviation hub of the Indian capital of New Delhi as well as the rest of northern India.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Washington Dulles International Airport, typically referred to as Dulles International Airport, Dulles Airport, Washington Dulles or simply Dulles, is an international airport in the Eastern United States, located in Loudoun County and Fairfax County in Virginia, 26 miles west of Downtown Washington, D.C.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: वाशिंगटन डलेस अंतर्राष्ट्रीय हवाई अड्डा, जिसे आमतौर पर डलेस अंतरराष्ट्रीय हवाई अड्डा, डलेस एयरपोर्ट, वाशिंगटन ड्यूलस या बस डलेस कहा जाता है, पूर्वी संयुक्त राज्य अमेरिका में एक अंतरराष्ट्रीय हवाई अड्डा है, जो वर्जीनिया में लाउडाउन काउंटी और फेयरफैक्स काउंटी में स्थित है, डाउनटाउन वाशिंगटन के 26 मील दूर, डी।

detailedDescription.articleBody: San Diego International Airport, formerly known as Lindbergh Field, is an international airport 3 mi northwest of Downtown San Diego, California, United States. It is owned and operated by the San Diego County Regional Airport Authority. The airport covers 663 acres of land.
